  "text": "Once the CTX drop evaporated and the worm emerged out of it, we started imaging (frame rate of 2 Hz). We then analyzed the movies using custom-made MATLAB software to extract neuron activity together with the worm position in relation to the chemical source. For accurate determination of worm trajectories, and to compensate for the wide-angle head swings during movement, we smoothed worm tracks ( Supplementary Fig. 18 ) with a smoothing spline, that uses a leastsquares approach with penalization for roughness [CITATION_1] 57 .",
